Method.СообщитьПользователю.Description=Generates and displays a message that may be associated with a form control element.
Method.СообщитьПользователю.Example.Description=1. To display a message at a managed form field bound to an object attribute\:\nCommonClient.NotifyUser(\nNStr("en \= 'Error message.'"), ,\n"FieldInObjectFormAttribute",\n"Object");\nAlternative usage in the object form\:\nCommonClient.NotifyUser(\nNStr("en \= 'Error message.'"), ,\n"Object.FieldInObjectFormAttribute");\n2. To display a message next to a managed form field bound to a form attribute\:\nCommonClient.NotifyUser(\nNStr("en \= 'Error message.'"), ,\n"FormAttributeName");\n3. To display a message related to an infobase object\:\nCommonClient.NotifyUser(\nNStr("en \= 'Error message.'"), InfobaseObject, "Responsible",,Cancel);\n4. To display a message by a reference to an infobase object\:\nCommonClient.NotifyUser(\nNStr("en \= 'Error message.'"), Reference, , , Cancel);\nIncorrect usage cases\:\n1. Passing the KeyData and PathToData parameters simultaneously.\n2. Passing a value of a type other than the allowed one in the KeyData parameter.\n3. Setting a reference without setting a field (and/or data path).
Method.СообщитьПользователю.Name=NotifyUser
Method.СообщитьПользователю.Param.КлючДанных.Description=infobase object or record key to which this message refers.
Method.СообщитьПользователю.Param.КлючДанных.Name=KeyData
